    "system": {
        "description": {
            "value": "<p><em>You visualize a scene within your mind, deftly twisting a piece of fleece to match the general shape of your illusion. Crushing the fleece in your hands, the illusion springs to life.</em></p><p dir=\"auto\" id=\"viewer-nmest4883\"><span><strong>Illusory Image</strong> </span></p><p><span>Roll an</span>&amp;Reference[illusoryimages]{illusion check}<span>for this spell.</span></p><ul><li><p>You create an illusion of an object, a creature, or some other visible phenomenon that is no larger than a 30-foot cube. You can also create illusory sounds, smells, and temperature. Your illusion cannot create an extreme temperature, loud sound, or otherwise extreme effect that would damage or otherwise harm a creature.</p></li><li><p><strong>Concentration:</strong> While within 120 ft. of the image, once on each of your turns, you can cause the image to move up to 30 ft. You can also adjust the sounds, smells, and temperature created by the illusion. The image shifts dynamically, and appears to be moving in a manner of your choosing (such as a person walking).</p></li></ul>",
            "chat": "<span>Roll an</span>&amp;Reference[illusoryimages]{illusion check}<span>for this spell.</span></p><ul><li><p>You create an illusion of an object, a creature, or some other visible phenomenon that is no larger than a 30-foot cube. You can also create illusory sounds, smells, and temperature. Your illusion cannot create an extreme temperature, loud sound, or otherwise extreme effect that would damage or otherwise harm a creature.</p></li><li><p><strong>Concentration:</strong> While within 120 ft. of the image, once on each of your turns, you can cause the image to move up to 30 ft. You can also adjust the sounds, smells, and temperature created by the illusion. The image shifts dynamically, and appears to be moving in a manner of your choosing (such as a person walking).</p></li></ul>"
        },
